Rebasing the commits of this branch on top of the base branch cannot be performed automatically due to conflicts encountered while reapplying the individual commits from the head branch.

@dvjyothsna there are a couple of options to verify json metadata:
1.  use table function to query from json thus your file does not need to have json extension;
2. modify file system plugin for this test to accept such files;
3. parse json code and verify its content.
